  "name": "RPlog_A_Deserted_Star_Destroyer",
  "title": "A Deserted Star Destroyer",
  "summary": "A military shuttle slips into the hangar of the Star Destroyer Predator, where Axel Vichten -- the self-proclaimed Lord Commander of the Sith Fleet -- receives the injured pilot Wolf, brought aboard from Tatooine at the behest of Lord Malign. Axel reveals the ship is no Imperial Navy vessel and presses Wolf on why Malign summoned him, while Wolf recognizes the Predator as a ship he served aboard years earlier. The conversation turns to old names: Axel confirms that Dareus, Wolf's former wingman, is aboard, and Wolf recounts how Danik Kreldin once tried to recruit him into a plot to assassinate the Emperor, a betrayal that still stings. As a medical droid scans Wolf's injuries, Axel explains that the Predator is crewed almost entirely by droids with few human or alien personnel, and floats the prospect of live-fire flight exercises once Wolf has healed. Axel notes he must still verify Wolf's status with Lord Malign before granting cockpit access, and Wolf follows the droid to a waiting bacta tank to recover.",
